BBK01.WT5002: Exchange rates on the Frankfurt exchange /FIM 100 = DM ... / Finland

General: Spot middle rates in Deutsche Mark; difference between buying or selling rate in D-Mark: 0.100 up to the end of 1993 / 0.080 since 1994.
